Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:25.71,SongJap,,0,0,0,,映し出す鏡に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:35.69,SongChn,,0,0,0,,幸福一定和悲哀很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:35.69,SongRom,,0,0,0,,{\K80}kit{\K60}to {\K30}shi{\K30}a{\K20}wa{\K20}se {\K200}wa {\K80}{\K60}ka{\K50}na{\K50}shi{\K50}mi {\K30}ni {\K30}ni{\K30}tei{\K90}ru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:35.69,SongJap,,0,0,0,,きっと幸せは 哀しみに似ている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.09,0:21:43.73,SongChn,,0,0,0,,闭上心灵的瞳眸
